data.description: Amazing opportunity next to all the attractions, restaurants, and shopping centers Orlando has to offer! An oversized corner lot pool home with potential to become your dream home or a great investment property. This 4-bed, 2-bath home is a hidden gem waiting to be uncovered. Nice sized bedrooms offer plenty of space for a growing family, with a fireplace in the living area for those cooler nights. Pool deck will need some rejuvenation, but can be transformed into your personal oasis for those hot Florida days. It has an open kitchen adjacent to a nice sized den. This beautiful home is a diamond in the rough, waiting for someone with a vision. Whether you're looking for a great family home or a savvy investment property, this is your chance to unlock its full potential. Don't miss out on this opportunity to shape your dream property–schedule a showing today!
